flowchart TD
    A[公理A] --> Core[颜色类/操作]
    B1[公理B.1] --> Core
    B2[公理B.2] --> Core
    C1[公理C.1-3] --> Amp[振幅函数]
    C4[公理C.4] --> Amp
    Amp --> Uni[幺正性]
    Uni --> AmpDet[振幅唯一确定]
    AmpDet --> Assoc[结合律]
    Assoc --> Operad[Operad存在性]
    Yoneda[Yoneda引理] --> OperadUniq[Operad唯一性]
    Core --> Indep[公理独立性]
    C4 --> C4Indep[公理C.4独立性]